cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with deep learning for dense matching and stereo estimation on aerial images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves robotics (cs.RO) as it deals with aerial images. The paper proposes a self-supervised training procedure, which is a machine learning technique (cs.LG). The paper also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it deals with deep learning. Finally, the paper involves graphics (cs.GR) as it deals with image processing.
